   text-text-main hover:text-sage hover:bg-sage-pale\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a></div><div class=\"relative\"><a class=\"px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.875rem] font-medium rounded-lg\n                    transition-all duration-150 block\n                    text-text-main hover:text-sage hover:bg-sage-pale\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 shrink-0\"><a class=\"hidden lg:inline-flex btn btn-primary btn-sm text-xs px-5\" href=\"/contact\">Get Advice</a><button class=\"lg:hidden p-2 rounded-lg text-bark hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main><section class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-100 py-14\"><div class=\"w-[min(1280px,100%-2rem)] mx-auto\"><span class=\"section-label block mb-2\">Policies</span><h1 class=\"text-bark\">Return &amp; Refund Policy</h1><p class=\"text-text-muted text-sm mt-2\">Last updated: January 2025</p></div></section><section class=\"py-14\"><div class=\"w-[min(1280px,100%-2rem)] mx-auto max-w-[800px]\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-12\"><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gray-100 text-center\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-sage-pale rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-sage mx-auto mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-text-muted mb-1\">Return Window</p><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-bark\">48 hours from delivery</p></div><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gray-100 text-center\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-sage-pale rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-sage mx-auto mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg></div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-text-muted mb-1\">Refund Time</p><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-bark\">Within 24 hours (M-Pesa)</p></div><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gray-100 text-center\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-sage-pale rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-sage mx-auto mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-text-muted mb-1\">Our Promise</p><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-bark\">Hassle-free for defects</p></div></div><div class=\"prose prose-sm max-w-none text-text-muted leading-relaxed [&amp;_h2]:font-display [&amp;_h2]:text-2xl [&amp;_h2]:text-bark [&amp;_h2]:mt-10 [&amp;_h2]:mb-4 [&amp;_h3]:font-semibold [&amp;_h3]:text-bark [&amp;_h3]:mt-6 [&amp;_h3]:mb-2 [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:pl-5 [&amp;_ul]:flex [&amp;_ul]:flex-col [&amp;_ul]:gap-1.5 [&amp;_p]:mb-4 [&amp;_strong]:text-bark [&amp;_strong]:font-semibold\"><h2>Our Return Policy</h2><p>We want you to be completely happy with your <!-- -->Feiwellhub Naturals<!-- --> purchase. If something isn&#x27;t right, we&#x27;ll do our best to make it right.</p><h2>What We Accept Returns For</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 not-prose my-6\"><div class=\"bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-green-100\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-600\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-green-700 text-sm\">Eligible for Return</h3></div><ul class=\"text-sm text-green-700 flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-disc pl-4\"><li>Damaged or defective products</li><li>Incorrect item received</li><li>Product significantly different from description</li><li>Tampered or compromised packaging</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-red-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-red-100\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-x text-red-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m15 9-6 6\"></path><path d=\"m9 9 6 6\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-red-700 text-sm\">Not Eligible</h3></div><ul class=\"text-sm text-red-700 flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-disc pl-4\"><li>Opened products (unless defective)</li><li>Change of mind after purchase</li><li>Products reported after 48 hours</li><li>Products not purchased from us</li></ul></div></div><h2>How to Request a Return</h2><ul><li>Contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of receiving your order</li><li>Send a WhatsApp message to <a href=\"https://wa.me/254715945238\" class=\"text-sage hover:underline\">+254 715 945 238</a> with your order number</li><li>Include a photo of the product showing the issue</li><li>We&#x27;ll respond within 2 hours during business hours</li></ul><h2>Refunds</h2><p>Once your return is approved:</p><ul><li><strong>M-Pesa refunds</strong> are processed within 24 hours</li><li><strong>Bank transfer refunds</strong> take 2–3 business days</li><li>Delivery fees are refunded if the error was on our side</li></ul><h2>Exchanges</h2><p>We&#x27;re happy to exchange a defective or incorrect product for the same item. If the item is out of stock, we&#x27;ll offer a full refund or credit towards another product.</p><h2>Contact Us</h2><p>For any return or refund queries, reach us on<!-- --> <a href=\"tel:+254 715 945 238\" class=\"text-sage hover:underline\">+254 715 945 238</a> <!-- -->or <a class=\"text-sage hover:underline\" href=\"/contact\">fill in our contact form</a>.</p></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-bark text-cream\"><div class=\"w-[min(1280px,100%-2rem)] mx-auto pt-16 pb-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-[1.8fr_1fr_1fr_1fr_1.4fr] gap-10 pb-10 border-b border-cream/10\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"Feiwellhub Naturals\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"82\" height=\"72\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\" object-contain brightness-0 invert sepia-[30%] saturate-[400%] hue-rotate-[10deg]\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ffeiwell-logo.94ea443d.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ffeiwell-logo.94ea443d.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ffeiwell-logo.94ea443d.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"leading-tight\"><span